Companhia de Locacao das Americas Seeks to Become Public Company in Brazil

-- B y   K a r e n   E e u w e n s
-- 
2011-10-10T07:37:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/companhia-de-locacao-das-americas-seeks-to-become-public-company-in-brazil.html
Cia. de Locacao das Americas, which
rents out utility trailers and recreational vehicles, filed a
request to register as a public company in  Brazil , according to
a posting on the website of securities regulator CVM.  After becoming a public company, it will be able to sell
securities in Brazil, including shares and debt.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karen Eeuwens in London at 
 keeuwens@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alan Purkiss at 
 apurkiss@bloomberg.net  